 setup and parameter selection, reducing setup time and increasing weld time. = Quick-access Auto-Set and pulse mode backlit buttons across the top illuminate when active = Soft-key buttons below the display change function depending on which screen is displayed \\u2014 makes setup or"}, {"source": "2024-int-catalog-Miller-Products.pdf", "doc_id": 32, "file_id": "1SZK4gC7R04nMtyK556SpCPid5WoH2uCL", "page": 6, "total_pages": 104, "collection": "banditosinc", "snippet": "\\u2018Be\\n\\nMillermatic 255 Ce with running gear\\n\\npackage shown.\\n\\n18 0 304\\n\\nEasy-to-understand interface with 7-inch color\\n\\nLCD display ensures proper machine setup and\\n\\nparameter selection, reducing setup time and\\n\\nincreasing weld time.\\n\\n= Quick-access Auto-Set and pulse mode backlit buttons across the top illuminate when active\\n\\n= Soft-key buttons below the display change function depending on which screen is displayed \\u2014 makes setup or change quick, easy and intuitive\\n\\n= Large text for easier readabi"}], "answer": "Yes, you can weld aluminum with a Millermatic 255. It is ideal for MIG welding aluminum and stainless steel, and it uses an optional XR-Aluma-Pro push-pull gun for aluminum welding (Source page 84)."}	POSITIVE
